data.description: Don’t miss this lovely home on a fabulous lot in Quail Brush Creek that backs to Stetson Hills open space and has Peak views. This two-story has an open great room concept featuring a living room with a gas fireplace that has a blower, a beautiful kitchen with a huge center island and glass front cabinets, an adjacent dining area that walks out to a 10 x 12 partially covered deck overlooking the open space and fully fenced backyard. The deck also has steps accessing the backyard. The backyard is filled with wild rose bushes, peonies, clematis and a custom built keystone garden bed. The second story features 3 bedrooms, all which have good sized walk-in closets and 2 baths and a huge family room loft area. The second upstairs bath has two sinks, there is a large closet in the family room for additional storage and the laundry room has upgraded insulation so when the washer or dryer are running the sound is muffled. The unfinished basement is garden level...light and bright for future expansion. The garage is a two-car with a tandem 3rd space for extra parking or a workshop area. Extras in the garage include a bike rack in the ceiling, tool wall mount and custom shelving. Additional upgrades include windowsills, rough-ins in the basement for a fourth bath and a wet bar, 4 exterior cameras, 2 indoor motion detectors, home alarm system, private office with french doors, slate kitchen appliances, walk-in pantry with an outlet to charge kitchen appliances, composite decking, lockable screen door off deck, utility tub in the laundry room, dimmer switches in the kitchen, dining room, loft and master bedroom, ceiling fans with remotes in the family room, loft and master bedroom, tile to the ceiling in both upstairs bathrooms, custom electrical outlet above the front porch for Christmas lights comfort height toilets, & raised counter tops in the master bath. The location of this home is one of a kind with open space behind, a green belt on the south side & views to the west.
